Social Development\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whaikaha will become more focused on policy and advocacy as a stand-alone agency.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1292, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Whaikaha\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"policy\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"advocacy\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"a stand-alone agency\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In other announcements, we have seenSimeon Brown pave the way for congestion chargingin conjunction with councils in cities where traffic moves too slowly, and they should be operating before the next election.\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1504, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other announcements\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"seenSimeon Brown\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"congestion chargingin conjunction\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"councils\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"cities\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"traffic\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"the next election\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1503}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been talked about for years.\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brown is doing something about it, with the caveat that it must be accepted by the public.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brown\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1566}, {\"ngram\": \"the caveat\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been fairly widely welcomed by the right, who like the concept of user pays, and the left, who want incentives to get 